OL,4,CPM pledges #430m for girls missing
OL,5,Ceducation amid aid row
OL,6, Boris Johnson at the G7 summit has
OL,7, pledged #430m to improve education in
OL,8, some of the world's poorest countries -
OL,9, with girls' education a priority.
OL,11,FThe prime minister said it was a source
OL,12,Fof "international shame" that so many
OL,13,Fgirls in poorer countries were missing
OL,14,Fout on access to school.
OL,16,FWith an education, these children could
OL,17,Fhave been "titans of industry or
OL,18,Fscientific pioneers", he said.
OL,20,FBut aid agencies called for a reversal
OL,21,Fof cuts to the UK's aid budget.
